    <item>
      <title>普华永道对古普塔（Gupta）的Wyelands银行的审计，由英国监管机构审核</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/pwc-fined-over-audit-of-gupta-s-wyelands-bank-by-uk-watchdog</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家英国监管机构罚款PriceWaterhouseCoopers LLP及其会计师之一，因为他们对Sanjeev Gupta的Wyelands Bank的有缺陷的审计，此前贸易财务专家Greenensill Capital崩溃了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/pwc-fined-over-audit-of-gupta-s-wyelands-bank-by-uk-watchdog</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 07:41:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本的Ishiba计划价格措施通过现有预算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ishiba-plans-powerful-inflation-measures-ahead-of-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理Shigeru Ishiba正在计划采取措施，以减轻通货膨胀对消费者的影响，这些消费者利用已经在当前和即将到来的会计年度预算中纳入的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/ishiba-plans-powerful-inflation-measures-ahead-of-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 06:44:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>东京法院命令解散与安倍谋杀案有关的教会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/tokyo-court-orders-dissolution-of-church-linked-to-abe-murder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京法院下令解散一个宗教团体，其筹款方法和与执政党政客的联系受到了两年多以前的前总理Shinzo Abe暗杀后受到审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/tokyo-court-orders-dissolution-of-church-linked-to-abe-murder</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 06:35:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国的达沃斯（Davos）提供了有关亚洲经济面临关税的乐观阅读</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-s-davos-offers-upbeat-read-on-asian-economy-facing-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据中国国际总理会议上的一份报告，即使美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）通过提高关税向国家施加压力的竞选活动升级，亚洲的经济将避免今年的经济放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/china-s-davos-offers-upbeat-read-on-asian-economy-facing-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 06:25:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
